{"tid":490719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[私煙]科學忍者隊柴灣拘捕馬國明","createTime":"2017-12-06T01:22:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T02:17:38.000Z","uid":131064,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"00115ebcd32ae1f90a37b8a1c94d928b0071355e","tid":490719,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/qa7pfNDGY72QhLVy9XNEVQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/4215e3d6a345299f7df010b2ddfa045b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fqa7pfNDGY72QhLVy9XNEVQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F4215e3d6a345299f7df010b2ddfa045b&h=7d039b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名貌似藝人馬國明的男子，在柴灣亂掉煙頭被食環署執法人員檢控。（設計圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能是本港最多人見證的垃圾蟲影片今日流出！一名貌似藝人馬國明的中年男子，日前神態自若站在柴灣街市行人天橋下的路旁吸煙，而他亦準備吸完最後一口煙後，就將煙蒂掉在地上。可惜橋上兩個穿着制服的食環職員早已鎖定目標，當他犯罪時上前檢控。而更證據確鑿的是，站在食環職員旁邊的街坊亦以第三身視角，將這次執法行動記錄下來。<br />\n<br />\n該段直擊食環執法的影片，今日(4日）上載於「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」，兩名穿着制服的食環職員一直目不轉睛看着橋下，原來他們已對橋下一個正在吸煙的男子虎視眈眈，他們在橋上觀察長達逾一分鐘。就在中年男子用腳踩熄煙蒂前一刻，橋上的二人隨即衝落橋配合橋下其他的執法人員，上前檢控男子。仍未知早已有人守株待兔的「柴灣馬明」，最終乖乖將身份證交出。而整個由守株待兔的檢控過程，原來更一早已被路人拍下，其後更放到網上。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民看過影片後都大讚食環職員，認為男子抵拉：「香港通街都係垃圾桶，行多兩步啫 ! 抵拉啦，如果係日本，煙頭都要吞落肚！」有人亦大讚路人拍片的影片精彩：「我一路睇片對食環職員好有代入感，一路等緊佢，究竟幾時掉煙頭，掉未？掉未？仲要吸多兩口？仲未掉？！」最終成功見證違法男子，或將要乖乖交出1500港元的罰款。東網正向食環署跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說<br />\n<br />\nLeon Ricky：拍片冇手震，時間啱啱好，片主是執法者？<br />\n<br />\nTopine Cheung：真係掉煙頭有樣睇。<br />\n<br />\nHo Mingi：我公司門口日日都有好多煙頭。<br />\n<br />\nNelson Yau：行動好成功，瓦解咗一個食煙人士。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E7%AB%99%E5%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%9F%E7%85%99%E9%A0%AD-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%A8%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%8B%E4%BD%A0-082334808.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25A9%258B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25B8%259F%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%25A8%2593%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259C%258B%25E4%25BD%25A0-082334808.html&d=Dj16aHTGWLAWY3FyFSabllzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=f77812d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E7%AB%99%E5%9C%A8%E6%A9%8B%E4%B8%8B%E4%B8%9F%E7%85%99%E9%A0%AD-%E9%A3%9F%E7%92%B0%E5%B0%B1%E5%9C%A8%E6%A8%93%E4%B8%8A%E7%9C%8B%E4%BD%A0-082334808.html</a>"},{"pid":"6d7fac76c3d227a73874a423f1693e36113eb85a","tid":490719,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:23:34.000Z","msg":"做乜抄我？<br />\n<br />\n食環出動科學忍者隊捉人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/489945/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/489945/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b11f53201765e018dea1ee1a8397f221640e9745","tid":490719,"uid":65743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:33:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食環本身都係仆街</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次花生狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0528ac3b7dc90b666855231e715f945ca30e45c7","tid":490719,"uid":150014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T02:17:38.000Z","msg":"似馬國明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}